                        </span>
                        <input id="q" name="q" type="search" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Rechercher un film ou une s√©rie‚Ä¶" class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-neutral-800 border border-white/10 text-sm placeholder-neutral-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-rose-500" />
